 ability to combine secure connectivity with advanced threat protection makes it an essential partner for protecting critical digital infrastructure.7. LevelBlueHeadquarters: Texas, USA​​​​​​​Chairman \\u0026 CEO: Robert McCullenRobert McCullen, Chairman \\u0026 CEO at LevelBlueLevelBlue is the world's largest pure-play managed security service provider, formed through the strategic combination of AT\\u0026T Cybersecurity and Trustwave.This powerful union brings together carrier-grade network visibility with elite forensic expertise and threat hunting capabilities.LevelBlue operates a global network of security operations centres and leverages the renowned SpiderLabs team to deliver industry-leading threat intelligence.Its unified platform integrates managed detection and response, consulting and security engineering to simplify cyber defence for complex enterprises.Holding critical government certifications like FedRAMP, LevelBlue is a trusted guardian for public sector agencies and global businesses seeking to reduce risk and close the security skills gap.6. NTT DATAHeadquarters: Tokyo, JapanPresident \\u0026 CEO: Yutaka SasakiYutaka Sasaki, President and CEO of NTT DATA GroupNTT DATA is a top-tier global innovator in IT and business services, possessing one of the world's largest cybersecurity operating platforms.Leveraging the immense network visibility of the NTT Group, it processes approximately 40% of the world's internet traffic, providing unparalleled predictive threat intelligence.NTT DATA operates a global ring of next-generation Cyber Defense Centres that utilise AI and automation to deliver autonomous security outcomes.Its portfolio covers the entire security lifecycle, from strategic consulting to 24/7 managed detection and response.A dominant force in Asia-Pacific and a major player globally, NTT DATA helps clients navigate the complexities of the digital economy with 'security as code' and robust data resilience solutions.5. Tata Consultancy Services